{"tid":2069165,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府推出「綠色生活本地遊鼓勵計劃」優化措施","createTime":"2020-06-18T07:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T07:54:40.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fe5f8c92c437a4dbd9e3bf3310dfb063e52b7612","tid":2069165,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T07:47:04.000Z","msg":"政府推出「綠色生活本地遊鼓勵計劃」優化措施 <br />\n2020-06-18 HKT 15:38<br />\n<br />\n明日起舉辦綠色生活本地遊的旅行代理商可獲加倍資助。<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局表示，在「綠色生活本地遊鼓勵計劃」優化措施下，旅行代理商接待每名參加者的鼓勵金，由原本100元增加至200元；每間旅行代理商可申請的人數上限，增加至1000名，每間旅行代理商可獲得的鼓勵金最高總額，亦由5萬元增至20萬元。<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華表示，群組聚集人數明日起會放寬至50人，新措施提供了良好契機，可以重新起動本地旅遊活動。<br />\n<br />\n由於計劃規定，本地遊需有餐飲及運輸元素，亦需要聘用持證導遊或領隊，相信措施亦能令相關業界受惠。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532800-20200618.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532800-20200618.htm&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHmFzq3Uwi%2FWN07E9MureYdc%3D&h=7b4d162a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532800-20200618.htm&h=6d3c30ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532800-20200618.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Good measure<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"58ca70ad9da154592c7d4a220452919c0d381d02","tid":2069165,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T07:54:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}